WEBVTT

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:16.042
Mommy...

00:00:17.083 --> 00:00:19.208
Mommy is... here.

00:00:21.375 --> 00:00:22.500
You're sure?

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:24.125
I'm certain.

00:00:24.125 --> 00:00:27.208
This player ID belongs to Mommy.

00:00:27.208 --> 00:00:30.625
The coordinates are right above us!

00:00:34.542 --> 00:00:35.708
Kirito!

00:00:37.167 --> 00:00:38.417
Wait!

00:00:38.417 --> 00:00:39.833
Kirito!

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:46.542
<i>Kirito, what's wrong?</i>

00:00:47.375 --> 00:00:52.000
<i>The person at the top of the World Tree</i>
<i>is that important to you?</i>

00:00:54.708 --> 00:00:58.625
Be careful, Kirito!
You're about to hit the barrier!

00:01:03.958 --> 00:01:05.042
Kirito!

00:01:07.208 --> 00:01:08.333
No!

00:01:12.542 --> 00:01:17.125
Stop it, Kirito. It's impossible!
You can't get any higher from here!

00:01:17.125 --> 00:01:18.542
I've got to go!

00:01:20.208 --> 00:01:22.250
I've got to go, can't you see?

00:01:24.667 --> 00:01:26.833
Mommy, it's me.

00:01:29.417 --> 00:01:32.042
Mommy!

00:01:33.583 --> 00:01:39.042
<i>The feelings I've hidden</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:01:39.042 --> 00:01:44.542
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:01:54.708 --> 00:02:05.042
<i>Seeking only a miracle, I wander</i>
<i>through an endless darkness</i>

00:02:05.208 --> 00:02:15.792
<i>If I stay here, I won't</i>
<i>ever see the future again</i>

00:02:15.875 --> 00:02:21.125
<i>Tonight the moon summons me again.</i>
<i>Though I still cannot speak,</i>

00:02:21.125 --> 00:02:24.917
<i>I keep crying out in my heart</i>

00:02:26.042 --> 00:02:31.292
<i>My hidden feelings</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:02:31.417 --> 00:02:36.333
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:42.125
<i>If I can stay stronger a bit longer,</i>

00:02:42.125 --> 00:02:48.208
<i>I will go beyond</i>
<i>this sky right in front of me</i>

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:56.542
<i>I will reach out towards</i>
<i>the future ahead of me</i>

00:03:02.083 --> 00:03:06.083
"The Grand Quest"

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.792
<i>Mommy...</i>

00:03:40.875 --> 00:03:42.000
<i>Mommy.</i>

00:03:42.333 --> 00:03:45.250
Y-Yui? Is that you?

00:03:45.250 --> 00:03:47.167
<i>Mommy! Mommy!</i>

00:03:47.333 --> 00:03:48.958
<i>I'm right here.</i>

00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:54.708
I'm up here...

00:03:55.417 --> 00:03:57.583
I'm right here, Yui!

00:04:00.958 --> 00:04:02.500
Kirito!

00:04:08.625 --> 00:04:09.875
Anything...

00:04:10.167 --> 00:04:13.250
Is there anything
I can drop down there?

00:04:17.875 --> 00:04:20.125
What is this, anyway?

00:04:20.125 --> 00:04:23.958
I tried to use warning mode
to contact her, but...

00:04:33.667 --> 00:04:34.875
What's that?

00:04:41.500 --> 00:04:42.708
A card?

00:04:43.042 --> 00:04:45.833
Leafa, do you know what this is?

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:49.375
No, I've never seen an item like that.

00:04:52.250 --> 00:04:54.042
No window, huh?

00:04:55.208 --> 00:04:56.208
This...

00:04:57.333 --> 00:05:00.125
This is a system-admin access code.

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.583
Then, can we use it
to access the GM controls?

00:05:04.583 --> 00:05:05.792
No...

00:05:06.583 --> 00:05:12.083
You need the appropriate console
to access it from within the game.

00:05:12.083 --> 00:05:15.417
Even I can't bring up
the system menu.

00:05:15.417 --> 00:05:16.500
I see.

00:05:18.167 --> 00:05:23.000
However, something like this wouldn't
just fall from the sky for no reason.

00:05:23.583 --> 00:05:25.125
This could be...

00:05:25.125 --> 00:05:26.167
Yes!

00:05:26.167 --> 00:05:29.750
Mommy must've heard us
and dropped it.

00:05:38.458 --> 00:05:39.708
<i>Asuna...</i>

00:05:46.667 --> 00:05:52.500
Leafa, tell me something. Where is the
gate that leads inside the World Tree?

00:05:53.250 --> 00:05:56.792
Well, it's in the dome
at the tree's base...

00:05:57.458 --> 00:06:03.833
B-But you can't get in! It's protected by guardians,
and even the biggest raids couldn't break through!

00:06:03.833 --> 00:06:06.042
Still, I have to go...

00:06:09.708 --> 00:06:12.625
Thank you so much
for everything.

00:06:13.708 --> 00:06:16.167
I'll be going the rest
of the way alone.

00:06:40.583 --> 00:06:41.792
Kirito...

00:06:50.625 --> 00:06:52.833
--Then let's go.
--Yeah.

00:06:53.917 --> 00:06:56.500
--Wh-What?
--Is this an event?

00:06:57.542 --> 00:07:00.542
Yui, do you know
the way to this dome?

00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:03.333
Yes, go up those stairs and...

00:07:06.792 --> 00:07:09.458
B-But are you sure, Daddy?

00:07:09.958 --> 00:07:16.333
The information so far indicates that breaking
through the gate will be very difficult.

00:07:16.333 --> 00:07:21.542
Our only choice is to try.
Even if we fail, it won't cost us our lives.

00:07:21.708 --> 00:07:23.750
That's true, but...

00:07:25.208 --> 00:07:30.625
And if I have to waste another second
just standing around, I'm going to go insane.

00:07:32.375 --> 00:07:35.583
And you want to see
Mommy soon, right?

00:07:36.125 --> 00:07:37.125
Yes.

00:08:12.458 --> 00:08:15.708
You who know not the heights of heaven...

00:08:16.292 --> 00:08:19.708
Do you desire passage to the king's castle?

00:08:21.375 --> 00:08:24.583
"Will you attempt the grand quest
'Guardians of the World Tree'?"
<i>I'm coming, Asuna.</i>

00:08:24.583 --> 00:08:26.542
<i>I'll be right there.</i>

00:08:26.542 --> 00:08:33.250
Then show that you are worthy of
letting your wings take flight.

00:08:42.250 --> 00:08:45.417
Let's go, Yui. Keep your head down.

00:08:45.750 --> 00:08:47.750
Good luck, Daddy.

00:09:39.083 --> 00:09:42.542
Let's go!

00:09:50.708 --> 00:09:53.208
Out of the way!

00:10:00.583 --> 00:10:02.125
<i>I can do this!</i>

00:10:37.375 --> 00:10:38.625
<i>Down you go.</i>

00:10:40.958 --> 00:10:43.708
<i>Down, damn it!</i>

00:11:39.542 --> 00:11:42.417
<i>Asuna! Asuna...</i>

00:11:42.792 --> 00:11:44.083
<i>Asuna...</i>

00:11:44.167 --> 00:11:46.417
<i>Asuna... Asuna...</i>

00:12:10.583 --> 00:12:11.917
<i>Just...</i>

00:12:11.917 --> 00:12:13.542
<i>Just a little more...</i>

00:12:38.042 --> 00:12:40.750
<i>Just a little more...</i>

00:12:54.500 --> 00:12:55.667
<i>Did I...</i>

00:12:58.167 --> 00:12:59.500
<i>Did I...</i>

00:13:00.333 --> 00:13:01.583
"Resurrection Timer"

00:13:01.583 --> 00:13:03.333
"Resurrection Timer"
...<i>die?</i>

00:13:07.500 --> 00:13:09.542
<i>Somewhere in my heart,</i>

00:13:10.208 --> 00:13:14.500
<i>I believed this world was just a game.</i>

00:13:16.375 --> 00:13:19.792
<i>Is this my punishment for that?</i>

00:13:21.250 --> 00:13:27.667
<i>My strength is nothing but skills and</i>
<i>status effects determined by numbers.</i>

00:13:29.375 --> 00:13:30.083
"Resurrection Timer"

00:13:30.083 --> 00:13:32.583
"Resurrection Timer"
<i>But I thought I could overcome</i>

00:13:33.667 --> 00:13:38.292
<i>the rules and limits of</i>
<i>the game and do anything.</i>

00:14:23.542 --> 00:14:26.583
A game where
you can die is too easy.

00:14:32.292 --> 00:14:33.417
<i>Asuna...</i>

00:14:45.833 --> 00:14:46.833
<i>No...</i>

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:48.083
<i>Stay back!</i>

00:15:08.042 --> 00:15:09.083
Kirito!

00:16:03.917 --> 00:16:05.458
Kirito...

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:10.917
"Spirit's Tear" "Glacial Chunk"
"World Tree Dewdrop"
"Stardust Sand" "Ancient Fruit"

00:16:27.042 --> 00:16:28.292
Kirito...

00:16:39.417 --> 00:16:42.875
--Thank you, Leafa.
--I-It was nothing...

00:16:42.875 --> 00:16:47.375
But don't ever do anything
reckless like that again. I'll be fine.

00:16:48.375 --> 00:16:52.417
--I don't want to cause you any more trouble.
--But it's not any...

00:16:52.583 --> 00:16:53.833
I...

00:16:58.875 --> 00:16:59.958
Kirito?

00:17:00.792 --> 00:17:03.875
W-Wait! You can't do it alone!

00:17:05.458 --> 00:17:07.333
You may be right...

00:17:07.500 --> 00:17:09.042
I am right! So...

00:17:09.042 --> 00:17:10.833
But I have to go.

00:17:14.167 --> 00:17:15.583
Stop...

00:17:15.583 --> 00:17:17.208
Just stop this.

00:17:17.625 --> 00:17:20.292
Go back to being your normal self.

00:17:20.750 --> 00:17:21.833
I...

00:17:22.792 --> 00:17:23.875
I...

00:17:24.083 --> 00:17:25.708
I care about you...

00:17:29.333 --> 00:17:30.417
Leafa...

00:17:33.958 --> 00:17:35.083
I'm sorry.

00:17:36.583 --> 00:17:39.375
If I don't get up there,
nothing will end.

00:17:39.375 --> 00:17:41.375
And nothing will begin.

00:17:41.708 --> 00:17:44.792
I have to see her... one more time.

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:47.833
To see Asuna one more time.

00:17:50.167 --> 00:17:52.000
What...

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:54.042
What did you just say?

00:17:54.042 --> 00:17:56.042
I said Asuna.

00:17:56.625 --> 00:17:57.042
"Asuna Yuki"

00:17:57.042 --> 00:17:59.500
That's the name of the person I'm looking for.

00:18:01.083 --> 00:18:03.792
But... then...

00:18:05.833 --> 00:18:06.917
Then...

00:18:07.500 --> 00:18:08.750
She is...

00:18:20.833 --> 00:18:23.208
Is that you, Big Brother?

00:18:27.250 --> 00:18:28.375
Sugu?

00:18:29.667 --> 00:18:31.000
Suguha?

00:18:33.083 --> 00:18:34.583
This is awful.

00:18:34.583 --> 00:18:36.042
This isn't fair...

00:18:36.500 --> 00:18:39.208
--It isn't...
--S-Sugu?

00:18:39.875 --> 00:18:40.708
"Are you sure you want to log out?"

00:18:41.083 --> 00:18:42.083
Sugu!

00:19:20.417 --> 00:19:22.458
Sugu, can I come in?

00:19:22.458 --> 00:19:23.833
Don't!

00:19:24.208 --> 00:19:25.750
Don't open the door.

00:19:26.875 --> 00:19:28.458
Leave me alone...

00:19:30.708 --> 00:19:33.000
What's wrong, Sugu?

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:35.667
I mean, I was surprised too.

00:19:35.917 --> 00:19:39.875
If you're mad I'm using the
NerveGear again, I apologize.

00:19:39.875 --> 00:19:42.583
But I didn't have a choice.

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:44.167
No...

00:19:44.708 --> 00:19:46.292
That isn't it.

00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:48.458
That isn't...

00:19:51.583 --> 00:19:52.708
Sugu?

00:19:53.875 --> 00:19:56.583
I... I...

00:19:57.125 --> 00:19:58.167
I...

00:19:59.125 --> 00:20:01.833
I betrayed my own heart!

00:20:02.000 --> 00:20:05.417
I betrayed my love for you...

00:20:06.333 --> 00:20:11.500
I was about to forget it all, to give it up.
To fall in love with Kirito...

00:20:11.750 --> 00:20:14.417
No, I already had!

00:20:14.917 --> 00:20:17.250
But...

00:20:18.917 --> 00:20:22.167
L-Love? But we're...

00:20:22.167 --> 00:20:23.375
I know.

00:20:23.958 --> 00:20:26.000
I already know!

00:20:26.333 --> 00:20:29.250
You and I aren't really siblings!

00:20:30.250 --> 00:20:33.958
I've known for the last two years.

00:20:35.208 --> 00:20:39.833
Wasn't the reason you quit kendo
and started avoiding me

00:20:39.833 --> 00:20:42.833
because you knew the whole time?

00:20:42.833 --> 00:20:46.917
You were distancing yourself
because I'm not your real sister, right?

00:20:46.917 --> 00:20:48.000
If so...

00:20:48.333 --> 00:20:51.625
Why are you
being nice to me now?

00:20:53.458 --> 00:20:59.417
I was so happy you
came back from SAO.

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:05.000
I was so happy you were being
nice to me, like when we were little.

00:21:05.333 --> 00:21:09.875
You were finally giving me a chance...
That's what I thought.

00:21:10.750 --> 00:21:11.958
But...

00:21:12.417 --> 00:21:16.583
If I'd known this would happen,
I wish you'd stayed cold to me.

00:21:17.833 --> 00:21:19.208
If you had,

00:21:19.542 --> 00:21:22.625
I wouldn't have realized
my feelings for you...

00:21:22.625 --> 00:21:25.875
Or been sad to learn
about Asuna...

00:21:26.875 --> 00:21:31.042
Or fallen in love with
Kirito instead of you!

00:21:36.375 --> 00:21:37.917
I'm sorry.

00:21:46.042 --> 00:21:48.583
Just... leave me alone...

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.333
Sugu...

00:22:17.875 --> 00:22:25.000
<i>Higher and higher,</i>
<i>I reach out my arms</i>

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:34.708
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:22:46.083 --> 00:22:52.833
<i>These endless feelings were</i>
<i>swallowed up into my daily life</i>

00:22:53.208 --> 00:23:00.042
<i>Swaying as they</i>
<i>change shape yet again</i>

00:23:00.417 --> 00:23:07.333
<i>Is it too late now? I ask</i>
<i>myself but receive no answer</i>

00:23:07.458 --> 00:23:15.000
<i>It's all up to me now,</i>
<i>both the ending and the beginning</i>

00:23:15.167 --> 00:23:22.125
<i>Higher and higher,</i>
<i>I reach out my arms</i>

00:23:22.125 --> 00:23:29.292
<i>I'm going to spread my wings</i>
<i>and head towards that gentle light</i>

00:23:29.292 --> 00:23:36.667
<i>Carrying the passion</i>
<i>I've lit in my heart</i>

00:23:36.667 --> 00:23:44.917
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:23:47.083 --> 00:23:53.195
Next Time: "Bonds."
